    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "looks like a race condition on close where the netstack is writing packets to a channel at the same time the channel is closed, I'll probably need to make sure that the tunnel is not being used at all (i.e. force close listeners and connections, etc.) before calling close on the netstack",
